Used the 1080p files i got from a mate,
and make a 480p release of it with some
work done to it :)
It got some cam shaking and some auto
focus issuses but i think it is
pretty watchable :)

Work Done: it was pretty dark so i 
started with trying to fix it, and
changed the colours a little bit, there
was a lot green in it but i would say
it turned out pretty nice.
Turned the saturation a little bit down,
changed levels a little bit.
and ran a noise removal filter.
Went a head and synced the audio should
be in sync now, might drop sometimes but
should go back in again.

Sample included
so yeah take it or leave it :)
